Class Paused

  • java.lang.Object
    • Paused

  • public class Paused
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is used to pause the game by writing the appropriate words below. This class contains Font and Fontmetric used to display the text in a desired manner. This class also contains the panel width and height pertaining to the game window size.
